2270:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @brief  Initializes the TIM One Pulse Time Base according to the specified
2271:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *         parameters in the TIM_HandleTypeDef and initializes the associated handle.
2272:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @note   Switching from Center Aligned counter mode to Edge counter mode (or reverse)
2273:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *         requires a timer reset to avoid unexpected direction
2274:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *         due to DIR bit readonly in center aligned mode.
2275:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *         Ex: call @ref HAL_TIM_OnePulse_DeInit() before HAL_TIM_OnePulse_Init()
2276:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  htim TIM One Pulse handle
